cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite the accompanying paper."
type: dataset
title: "coordination-traces-100: LLM Multi-Agent Coordination Traces on 100 Prediction Markets"
abstract: >
  Full reasoning traces for five LLM multi-agent coordination configurations
  evaluated on 100 resolved Polymarket binary prediction markets. Accompanies
  "Coordination as an Architectural Layer for LLM-Based Multi-Agent Systems"
  (Nechepurenko & Shuvalov, 2026).
authors:
